Date:   Fri Feb 21 00:13:00 2020 -0500

    added note about memory models to Makefile.wat
    
    use FAR_LINES for all models in sysdep.h even if SMALL is not defined.

commit f6a63db7f0dc1bfacb8cd593082afd17c0f2dd3f
